### Issue Tracking

- None

### Make PyPi Update

1. Update version

2. ```sh
   rm -rf dist
   python3 -m build
   pip install -e .
   python3 -m twine upload --verbose -r testpypi dist/*
   ```

### Run Tests

```sh
pytest ./tests --log-level=INFO -rx -l -x; rm -rf tables
```

### Show Logs

```sh
sudo docker logs -f --since=15m -t app_name
```

